social_posts.post_text: This bathroom! Perfect tones and textures at the new @ilbraccopostoak in Houston. Lots of great details in this one. Designed by @hsuoffice // #interiors

social_posts.post_text: Bringing some sunshine on this cloudy day in Austin. Big congrats to @thelorenhotels for making @travelandleisure 2023 “It List” for best new hotels in the world! Swipe for more // #tlpicks

First stop was just a block away for some cocktails at @aasb.distillery. The vibe was so nice! They distill their own vodka and gin and we got two seasonal specials:

I got the Thai Iced Tea with gin, coconut cream, cardamom bitters and sea salt spray.

If you know Lauren, the Underwood Martini was right up her alley. It was a play on a dirty martini with umami tincture and garnished with a candied mushroom. // @cityofsantafe #thecitydifferent

Spring in Santa Fe! 🌸 We had a blast this morning on our bike tour of the city with @heritageinspirations. 

Our guide took us to numerous places around the city to learn more about the history of Santa Fe, but my favorite was scenic stretch along the river! // #thecitydifferent

A few snaps from the multi sensory experience that is @meow__wolf Santa Fe.

In all honesty, Lauren and I were a bit skeptical about how much we would enjoy the visit, but it blew our minds! The attention the detail and sheer number of installations was so fun to explore. We spent two hours wondering through the spaces and time flew by. Swipe for more and check out my stories for videos! // #thecitydifferent

I forgot to pack my sketchbook, but I grabbed a notecard before we headed out and did a quick scribble to remember our trip.

Thank you @hotelsantafe.nm for such a great stay! // #thecitydifferent @cityofsantafe

I know this 12’ x 12’ space doesn’t look like much but it’s been a game changer for us the past year. We added a second story dormer above the garage which overlooks a 12 acre park out front. I’m sharing some progress photos on my stories, check them out for more! // #roomandboard
